In the event of termination, your account will be disabled, and you may not be granted access to your account or any files or other content contained in your account although residual copies of information may remain in our system. GQueues accounts with paid licenses will not display advertisements and the content of paid accounts will not be used for the purpose of targeting advertisements. Additional Terms of Use for GQueues Subscriptions (End User License Agreement) The following terms and conditions apply to all GQueues subscription accounts. ACCEPTANCE OF GQUEUES TERMS OF USE By using the full version of GQueues and/or submitting payment for an annual subscription, you agree to these Additional Terms that supplement the GQueues Terms of Use located above. GQueues reserves the right to update and change, from time to time, these Additional Terms and all documents incorporated by reference. DESCRIPTION OF FEATURES The full version of GQueues provides subscribers with all of the features of GQueues Lite, plus Google Calendar integration, assignments, collaboration, reminders, and additional functionality that may be added at a later date. PAYMENT TERMS General Terms - If you are purchasing a GQueues subscription, you will be charged automatically and immediately using the payment method you have selected. All currency references are in U.S. dollars. Payment for Subscription - Payment occurs on a pre-pay basis and you will be charged for the one year price upfront. Subscriptions will automatically renew as specified at the time of initial checkout. You can turn off auto-renew for your subscription by following these steps for individual subscriptions or these steps for domain subscriptions. If you turn off auto-renew, near the expiration of your annual subscription, you will be prompted to renew your GQueues subscription, at which time you may elect to continue your annual subscription. If you do not elect to renew your GQueues subscription, your account will automatically revert to a free GQueues Lite account upon the expiration of your GQueues subscription. Cancellation of Subscription - Please note, unless GQueues gives notice to the contrary, that payment for subscriptions is non-refundable. If you cancel your subscription before the end of the term for which you paid, your cancellation will take effect immediately, and you will not be given any refund. Termination - If your payment is invalid for any reason, your GQueues account will revert to a free GQueues Lite account; provided, however, that GQueues reserves the right to cancel your account entirely in such case, whereupon all the information and content contained within it may be deleted permanently. GQueues accepts no liability for information or content that is deleted due to an invalid payment. GQUEUES' RESERVATION OF RIGHTS GQueues expressly reserves the right to immediately modify, delete content from, suspend, or terminate your account and refuse current or future use of any GQueues version, including GQueues Lite, if GQueues, in its sole discretion, believes you have: (i) violated or tried to violate the rights of others; or (ii) acted inconsistently with the spirit or letter of the Terms of Use or these Additional Terms. In such event, your GQueues account may be suspended or cancelled immediately in GQueues' sole discretion, all the information and content contained within it deleted permanently, and you will not be entitled to any refund of any of the amounts you have paid for such account. GQueues accepts no liability for information or content that is deleted.
